David GOTHARD, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Kevin RAMBOSK, Collier County Sheriff, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-3519 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. September 19, 2017
